---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Prijzen | Transparante AI-Abonnementen vanaf €79/mnd | Vexai"
  description="Bekijk de prijzen van Vexai's Chat AI en Telefoon AI. Vanaf €79 per maand. Geen verborgen kosten. Inclusief setup, onboarding en support."
  bodyBg="#f9f9f9"
>

  <main class="bg-surface font-body text-body text-on-surface pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-20 md:pb-32">

    <!-- HERO -->
    <section class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-6 flex flex-col items-center text-center mt-8 md:mt-12 mb-[80px] md:mb-[150px]">
      <h1 class="font-h1 text-h1 text-on-surface max-w-[900px] mb-6 md:mb-8" data-i18n="pri.h1">
        Automatiseer je klantenservice met slimme AI
      </h1>
      <p class="font-body text-body text-on-surface-variant max-w-[620px] mb-10 md:mb-12" data-i18n="pri.hero_p">
        Mis nooit meer een kans. Laat onze Chat AI en Telefoon AI 24/7 je chats beantwoorden en telefoontjes afhandelen alsof het een echte medewerker is
      </p>
      <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center gap-4 mb-16 md:mb-24 w-full sm:w-auto">
        <a class="bg-primary text-on-primary font-button text-button px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity w-full sm:w-auto text-center" href="/contact/" data-i18n="pri.cta1">Plan een adviesgesprek</a>
        <a class="bg-transparent border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-button text-button px-8 py-4 rounded-full hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors w-full sm:w-auto text-center" href="#prijzen" data-i18n="pri.cta2">Bekijk de prijzen</a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRODUCT OVERVIEW CARDS -->
    <section class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-6 mb-[80px] md:mb-[150px]">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-on-surface mb-4" data-i18n="pri.overview_h2">Kies de AI-oplossing die bij je past</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-on-surface-variant max-w-[600px] mx-auto" data-i18n="pri.overview_p">
          Transformeer hoe je communiceert met je klanten door gebruik te maken van onze geavanceerde taalmodellen
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5 md:gap-6">
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full">
          <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-container h-32 md:h-40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-outline group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">record_voice_over</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-h3 text-h3 text-on-surface mb-2 text-xl">Chat AI</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-grow">Functies: 24/7 livechat, antwoordt binnen seconden, koppeling met je eigen kennisbank (FAQ), leads verzamelen.</p>
          <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline inline-flex items-center" href="/chat-ai/">
            Ontdek Chat AI&nbsp;<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] ml-1">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full">
          <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-container h-32 md:h-40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-outline group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">graphic_eq</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-h3 text-h3 text-on-surface mb-2 text-xl">Telefoon AI</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-grow">Functies: Automatische telefonische opname, spreekt vloeiend Nederlands, plant direct afspraken in je agenda, stuurt na het gesprek een samenvatting per mail.</p>
          <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline inline-flex items-center" href="/telefoon-ai/">
            Ontdek Telefoon AI&nbsp;<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] ml-1">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 hover:shadow-sm transition-shadow duration-300 group flex flex-col h-full sm:col-span-2 lg:col-span-1">
          <div class="mb-6 bg-surface-container h-32 md:h-40 rounded-xl overflow-hidden flex items-center justify-center">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-4xl text-outline group-hover:text-primary transition-colors">content_copy</span>
          </div>
          <h3 class="font-h3 text-h3 text-on-surface mb-2 text-xl">Allebei (All-in-One AI Assistent)</h3>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-sm leading-relaxed mb-4 flex-grow">Functies: Volledige dekking. Je mist geen enkele chat én geen enkel telefoontje meer. Data wordt centraal gesynchroniseerd.</p>
          <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline inline-flex items-center" href="/contact/">
            Ontdek All-in-One&nbsp;<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] ml-1">arrow_forward</span>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- PRICING SECTION -->
    <section id="prijzen" class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-6 mb-[80px] md:mb-[150px]">
      <div class="text-center mb-12 md:mb-16">
        <h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-on-surface mb-4" data-i18n="pri.pricing_h2">Eenvoudige, transparante prijzen</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-on-surface-variant max-w-[600px] mx-auto" data-i18n="pri.pricing_p">
          Kies het plan dat het beste aansluit bij de groei van jouw onderneming
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row gap-5 md:gap-6 justify-center items-stretch">
        <!-- Chat AI -->
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-on-surface mb-2">Chat AI</h3>
          <div class="mb-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">Vanaf </span>
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface">€79</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant"> / mnd</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-outline mb-6 md:mb-8 font-medium">+ €1200,- eenmalige setup fee</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-6 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Centraal dashboard voor alle contacten</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Afspraken automatisch in jouw agenda</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Koppeling met Website &amp; WhatsApp</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Volledige Chat AI functionaliteit</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact/" class="w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-full border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-button text-button hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-center block">Plan adviesgesprek</a>
        </div>
        <!-- Telefoon Assistent -->
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col">
          <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-on-surface mb-2">Telefoon Assistent</h3>
          <div class="mb-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">Vanaf </span>
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface">€199</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant"> / mnd</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-outline mb-6 md:mb-8 font-medium">+ €1500,- eenmalige setup fee</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-6 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Inclusief 300 belminuten per maand</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Gekoppeld aan je huidige nummer</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Directe agenda-koppeling</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Volledige technische integratie</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact/" class="w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-full border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-button text-button hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-center block">Vraag demo aan</a>
        </div>
        <!-- All-in-One (FEATURED) -->
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-high border-2 border-primary rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col relative lg:-translate-y-4 shadow-lg">
          <div class="absolute top-0 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 bg-primary text-on-primary text-[10px] font-bold px-3 py-1 rounded-full uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap">POPULAIRSTE KEUZE</div>
          <div class="mt-2 mb-2">
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-on-surface">All-in-One AI</h3>
            <p class="text-xs font-medium text-primary uppercase tracking-wider">Chat + Telefoon</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-1">
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant">Vanaf </span>
            <span class="text-4xl font-bold text-on-surface">€249</span>
            <span class="text-sm font-normal text-on-surface-variant"> / mnd</span>
          </div>
          <div class="text-xs text-primary mb-6 md:mb-8 font-semibold">+ €1999,- setup fee (Bespaar €701!)</div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-6 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Inclusief alle Chat AI functies</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Inclusief alle Telefoon AI functies</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Eén centraal dashboard</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Prioritaire onboarding &amp; support</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact/" class="w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-full bg-primary text-on-primary font-button text-button hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity text-center block">Claim All-in-One deal</a>
        </div>
        <!-- Enterprise -->
        <div class="flex-1 bg-surface-container-lowest border border-outline-variant rounded-[20px] md:rounded-[24px] p-6 md:p-8 flex flex-col">
          <div class="mb-6">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-on-surface leading-tight">Enterprise</h3>
            <p class="text-sm font-medium text-on-surface-variant">Maatwerk</p>
          </div>
          <div class="mb-6 md:mb-8">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-on-surface">Op aanvraag</div>
          </div>
          <ul class="space-y-3 md:space-y-4 mb-6 md:mb-8 flex-grow">
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Voor bedrijven met extreem hoge volumes</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Maatwerk koppelingen met CRM-systemen (Salesforce, Exact, etc.)</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">Dedicated AI-trainer voor jouw specifieke bedrijfsprocessen</span></li>
            <li class="flex items-start"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary mr-3 text-[18px]">check_circle</span><span class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant leading-snug">SLA-garanties en premium enterprise support</span></li>
          </ul>
          <a href="/contact/" class="w-full py-3 px-4 rounded-full border border-outline-variant text-on-surface font-button text-button hover:bg-surface-container transition-colors text-center block">Bespreek Maatwerk</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- TRUST SECTION -->
    <section class="max-w-[1280px] mx-auto px-5 md:px-6 mb-[80px] md:mb-[150px] grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 md:gap-12 items-center border-y border-surface-variant py-[60px] md:py-[80px]">
      <div class="flex flex-col space-y-5 md:space-y-6">
        <h2 class="font-h2 text-h2 text-on-surface" data-i18n="pri.trust_h2">Betrouwbaar, veilig en klaar voor groei</h2>
        <p class="font-body text-body text-on-surface-variant" data-i18n="pri.trust_p">
          Wij zorgen voor een waterdichte installatie van jouw AI-assistenten. Jouw bedrijfsdata en klantgegevens zijn bij ons in veilige handen.
        </p>
        <a class="text-sm font-medium text-primary hover:underline inline-flex items-center" href="/contact/">
          Plan een vrijblijvend gesprek <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-[16px] ml-1">arrow_forward</span>
        </a>
      </div>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 md:gap-4">
        <div class="border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-28 md:h-32">
          <span class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 text-base md:text-lg">GDPR / AVG</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Volledig compliant</span>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-28 md:h-32">
          <span class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 text-base md:text-lg">99.9% Uptime</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Optimale bereikbaarheid</span>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-28 md:h-32">
          <span class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 text-base md:text-lg">SSL Beveiligd</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Geëncrypteerde verbinding</span>
        </div>
        <div class="border border-outline-variant rounded-xl p-5 md:p-6 bg-surface-container-lowest flex flex-col items-center justify-center text-center h-28 md:h-32">
          <span class="font-bold text-on-surface mb-1 text-base md:text-lg">Dagelijkse Back-ups</span>
          <span class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant">Jouw data altijd veilig</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>
</Layout>
